      "rationale": "Validation experiments used porcine blood at hematocrit 33% ± 2% in a recirculating loop at CPB-representative flow rates (3–7 L/min) and rotational speeds (2000–4000 RPM). Fluid properties and operating envelope match COU specification. Validation domain adequately spans the COU operating space."
