      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published benchmark comparisons for centrifugal pump internal flows. Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model applied with coefficients from Heuser and Opitz (1980). Model form uncertainty estimated via comparison of two hemolysis model variants; difference < 8% in predicted NIH. Model form adequacy confirmed for MRL 2."
